Power of the P-test

power_of_P_test.Rd

Compute the power of the P-test under specific settings

power_of_P_test(setting = "ux", N, C)

Arguments

setting

the distribution of null and alternative
N

sample size, can be a vector
C

constant parameter, can be a vector

Value

power table

Examples

power_of_P_test('ux',c(10,20,30),c(0.2,0.3))
